

=Bio=

"Joy is a StreetArtist and Designer in Hanover/Germany. He´s interested and contributes to Social Sculptures, Shareconomy, Social Capital, Transition Towns, and cultural bottom-up approaches of any kind.

Main project since 1997 is the (co)creation of an autarkic, sustainable, floating habitat out of globalized waste and renewable local materials. Started at the world fair EXPO2000 in Germany, fhe main construction site for "asap-island" is in Goa/India since 2012." 


